{"tid":1005874,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB八點半做緊個齣算唔算2018度最撚閪煩電影劇？","createTime":"2019-02-02T13:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T14:57:01.000Z","uid":62597,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cb0926960af965cb653ee8e14e950100201511d5","tid":1005874,"uid":62597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:53:51.000Z","msg":"利申左先 平時唔睇tvb <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係返左屋企老豆老母係度睇先知做緊呢齣唔知保險乜春<br />\n<br />\n岩岩聽左一個鐘呢齣野 （因為用緊電腦做野）<br />\n發覺有50%時間都係播佢份唔岩音既主題曲<br />\n點解一集可以一半時間都播歌咁撚煩 又唔係唱得好聽 又唔岩音 真係好比主能夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最撚癡線係播完廣東話版本 再播<span style=\"font-size: large;\">普</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">通</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">話</span>版本！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底呢齣劇個導演監製係咪short撚左呀？定係開創緊一個播主題曲仲多過演員對白既先河？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2938a2cc589b6eb106a626a82e0fde69d297b1","tid":1005874,"uid":69621,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T13:55:44.000Z","msg":"默契依然"},{"pid":"bb8452c45ea1bb3974ff4018945635cf9d148b8e","tid":1005874,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:15:58.000Z","msg":"唔止主題曲。套野d人講下野都係咁彈琴。聽都聽唔清楚d人up乜"},{"pid":"2d8d7e02477c3979d225b7343c1b921c12205c5d","tid":1005874,"uid":224452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:21:09.000Z","msg":"史上最戇鳩電視劇"},{"pid":"f1537ad17d5744fa72bb9e7c433693e1adb1a879","tid":1005874,"uid":62597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:21:43.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味又播<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220e1fc2c69d33ae07d5fd58233bfd98ac737196","tid":1005874,"uid":12944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:23:21.